
Problem : If you had deposited a coin on the cryptocurrency exchange that brought 7% fixed profit daily for a week, how much wCould your $ 1000 reach at the end of the 7th day?

money = 1000
rate_per_day = 0.07
day = 7
result_money = money * (rate_per_day + 1) ** day
print(f'The amount of money which end of 7th day is ${result_money}')

The amount of money which end of 7th day is $1605.7814764784307
